00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.370
In this exercise, we'd like you to take what you know about looping and turtles,
在这次演习中我们想让你了解循环和海龟

00:00:05.370 --> 00:00:07.155
and draw something of your own.
把你自己的东西画出来

00:00:07.155 --> 00:00:10.919
But specifically, we've given you a list of the colors
但具体来说 我们给了你一份颜色列表

00:00:10.919 --> 00:00:14.775
of the rainbow and we'd like you to draw something rainbow colored.
我们希望你能画出彩虹色的东西

00:00:14.775 --> 00:00:19.685
You can use a loop over this list to draw a shape with different colored sides.
您可以在此列表上使用循环来绘制具有不同颜色边的形状 

00:00:19.684 --> 00:00:24.009
